title: Photo Professional Issue 94 - 2014  UK
description:
Photo Professional Issue 94 - 2014  UK

108 Pages | PDF | English | 24 MB 


The latest issue of Photo Professional showcases the stunning high-speed photographs of Thomas Morel, while our usual mix of stories sees us reporting on a rather special wedding workshop hosted by Adam Duckworth, Trevor Yerbury explaining why he believes the portrait market is so crucial, and Jerry Ghionis banging the drum for well-targeted marketing.
